
- Requirement: a C++ compiler with C++11 support.

  The following compilers have been tested:
    - GCC 4.8.2 (GNU/Linux x86_64).
    - LLVM/Clang 3.3 (GNU/Linux x86_64).
    - MSVC 2013 Express (Windows 7 x86_64).

- Build (GNU/Linux):

  mkdir build
  cd build
  cmake -D CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release ..
  make

- Test (GNU/Linux):

  ../scripts/test.sh 'Hello world.'
